Privacy Policy for TICKETVISOR

This Privacy Policy outlines how TICKETVISOR collects, uses, and protects the personal information of its users. By using TICKETVISOR, you consent to the practices described in this policy.

Information Collection: TICKETVISOR may collect certain information from users to provide and improve its services. This information may include Discord user IDs, server information, ticket details, and any other data necessary for the ticket management functionality.

Data Usage: The information collected by TICKETVISOR is used solely for the purpose of providing the ticket management features within Discord. This includes creating, assigning, tracking, and closing support tickets efficiently. TICKETVISOR does not share or sell personal information to third parties.

Data Storage: TICKETVISOR stores user data in secure databases. We take reasonable measures to protect the information against unauthorized access, loss, or alteration. However, please note that no data transmission over the internet or electronic storage method can be guaranteed to be 100% secure.

Third-Party Services: TICKETVISOR may utilize third-party services, such as hosting providers and analytics tools, to support its functionality. These third-party services may have access to certain user data but are strictly bound by their own privacy policies and data protection practices.

Cookies: TICKETVISOR may use cookies or similar technologies to enhance the user experience and collect usage information. Cookies are small text files stored on a user's device. You may modify your browser settings to refuse cookies, but this may affect the functionality of TICKETVISOR.

Children's Privacy: TICKETVISOR is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we become aware that we have inadvertently gathered information from a child, we will take steps to delete it as soon as possible.

Data Retention: TICKETVISOR retains user data only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected and to comply with legal obligations. Once the data is no longer required, it will be securely deleted.

Changes to the Privacy Policy: We reserve the right to modify or update this Privacy Policy at any time. We will notify users of any material changes via a notice on the TICKETVISOR website or through other appropriate means. Continued use of TICKETVISOR after any modifications constitutes your acceptance of the updated Privacy Policy.

Contact Information: If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or the use of your personal information, please contact us at mail@okaysahin.com

